<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV38">
<l>kaṭaṅkalanta vaṉkarima ruppocittor poykaivāy</l>
<l>viṭaṅkalanta pāmpiṉmēṉa ṭampayiṉṟa nātaṉē</l>
<l>kuṭaṅkalanta kūttaṉāya koṇṭalvaṇṇa taṇṭuḻāy</l>
<l>vaṭaṅkalanta mālaimārpa kālanēmi kālaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord who danced on the poisonous snake in a pond,</l>
<l>Having broken the tusk of a mighty elephant with a rut flower!</l>
<l>O cloud-hued [Lord] who dance with pots!</l>
<l>O [Lord] whose chest appears with strings of cool tulasi garlands!</l>
<l rend="indent">O Kālanemi’s death!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
